LDAP filter:
---------------------------------------
(&(&(objectClass=sudoRole)
    (|(cn=rule1)
      (cn=rule2)
    )
  )
  (|(!(sudoHost=*))
    (sudoHost=ALL)
    (sudoHost=client1.example.cz)
    (sudoHost=client1)
    (sudoHost=192.168.0.2)
    (sudoHost=192.168.0.0/24)
    (sudoHost=fe80::a00:27ff:fea1:b983)
    (sudoHost=fe80::/64)
    (sudoHost=+*)
    (|(sudoHost=*\\\\*)
      (sudoHost=*?*)
      (sudoHost=*\\**)
      (sudoHost=*[*]*)
    )
  )
)

SYSDB filter:
---------------------------------------
(&(objectClass=sudoRule)
  (|(cn=test4)
    (cn=test5)
  )
)
